Package com.ziluck.factions.base.struct

All enums for configuring Factions and Users.

See: Description

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Access
    The level of access a User has to a certain Action within a Faction.
    Action
    An Action is something a User is able to do relating to their Faction.
    ChatMode
    Represents where a User is talking to.
    FactionType
    Represents the purpose for each Faction.
    Flag
    All flags that can be attributed to a Faction.
    Permission
    Permissions that Users must have in order to interact with the plugin.
    Relation
    The relationships two Factions can have with one another.
    Role
    Represents the role that a User takes in a Faction.
